{"tid":1416213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"暑假就完 時間冇多！(小弟愚見)","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:46:46.000Z","uid":280717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f82fbe01c65970b2700ca89ccf2a1c3b1dd1df8","tid":1416213,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"暑假一完咗大家都要返工返學<br />\n政府真係拖多陣就完美離場<br />\n但係我想講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">快</span></strong>！但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好急</span></strong>！！</span><br />\n<br />\n前線你哋就好似人民英雄咁<br />\n但英雄同私刑者只係一線之差<br />\n要記住自己係背負住香港嘅各大訴求<br />\n反送中 放義士 警黑勾結 軍政府 雙普選 等等...<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得以前嘅民意點嚟？<br />\n係和理非勇武合作 缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n大家不彷稍作休息 做個Last battle！<br />\n比文宣組搞個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鋪天蓋地嘅宣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外 前兩次都係<br />\n如果有人肯正正式式宣讀一啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宣言</span></span>(eg佔立法會)<br />\n都會做成好大正面回響！尤其中英雙語<br />\n<br />\n至於最後行動係點希望真係傾下商量下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n香港是我家，全城守護它。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b361a91b31b3a8472549a20c7c7021f13b99bec5","tid":1416213,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:46:43.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"325d069e6069bbb7e0b558ad671c4c9d5c18bfb3","tid":1416213,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"自推x9"},{"pid":"5d2f473609bd024986fcbb168d9b85620b75d707","tid":1416213,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"自推x8"},{"pid":"7c4f9672d26ee17ab3326bb037c2efa21a97d4da","tid":1416213,"uid":280717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"自推x7"},{"pid":"0def61427d2e3c5a275f76a083f99898d2dd0146","tid":1416213